w:r.w:t: ALGAALGA is dedicated to supporting European municipalities and countries in their efforts to achieve and implement climate targets. Our mission is twofold: to provide innovative solutions that address imminent climate change-related challenges and to facilitate the reduction of net carbon dioxide emissions for client companies. By leveraging advanced technologies in biomass production, ALGAALGA aims to contribute significantly to the global fight against climate change.

ALGAALGA's system enables client companies to significantly reduce their net carbon dioxide emissions. This reduction not only helps in meeting regulatory requirements but also lowers the costs associated with emission allowances. Our technology offers orders of magnitude more efficient biomass production per unit area of land compared to traditional methods, thereby maximizing resource utilization and minimizing environmental footprint.
: Our primary product offering consists of
and optimized CCU units in the form of modular microalgae bioreactors. These bioreactors are designed to capture carbon dioxide efficiently and convert it into valuable biomass.
: Each bioreactor can be tailored to meet the specific needs of the client, ensuring optimal performance and integration with existing systems.
: We offer comprehensive maintenance contracts to ensure the continuous and efficient operation of our bioreactors.
: By providing ongoing support, we aim to build long-term partnerships with our clients, ensuring sustained benefits and operational excellence.

: In addition to the sale of bioreactors, ALGAALGA offers a service model that includes the harvesting and sale of the produced biomass. This biomass can be utilized by third-party companies for carbon-neutral fuel production or as livestock feed.
: This service model not only provides an additional revenue stream for our clients but also contributes to the circular economy by repurposing captured carbon dioxide into valuable products.
